{"tid":639254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泛民莫乃光:慶幸王沒有發表撕裂香港言論  考慮入中聯辦","createTime":"2018-04-23T10:39:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T11:32:58.000Z","uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a79f1323572453589984fd20808290d71996533c","tid":639254,"uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T10:39:30.000Z","msg":"中聯辦主任王志民應邀出席立法會午宴，專業議政成員莫乃光說，慶幸王志民沒有再發表撕裂香港的言論，又表示若王志民邀請立法會議員到中聯辦，他們會考慮應邀。<br />\n<br />\n專業議政成員莫乃光、葉建源、梁繼昌、郭榮鏗及邵家臻，席間向王志民提交信件，內容包括重申保障港人思想自由的重要性、要求重啟政改等，其中邵家臻另外提交關於單程證批核權的信件，梁繼昌就希望王志民花時間了解立法會工作。"},{"pid":"d2cb8f920ec9b237bc32dba49f84727533aabb47","tid":639254,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T11:00:42.000Z","msg":"王：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n飯民：阿爺無出聲呀，好彩啫，好開心"},{"pid":"0f1da2d2b2b5af77315b53b583427e2890f4f030","tid":639254,"uid":38666,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T11:29:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20100525/photo/0525-00174-001h1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20100525%2Fphoto%2F0525-00174-001h1.jpg&h=82d68697&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c33082b3389431b2e4c42a797de92dc4dea0209","tid":639254,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f1da2d2b2b5af77315b53b583427e2890f4f030","tid":639254,"uid":38666,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T11:29:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20100525/photo/0525-00174-001h1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20100525%2Fphoto%2F0525-00174-001h1.jpg&h=82d68697&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/d